data.title: Chelsea Handler
data.text:
In a democracy, voting is one of the most powerful ways to use your voice. Vote411.org provides comprehensive, nonpartisan election information including election dates, registration requirements and deadlines, polling locations, candidate information, and online voters' guides. Click here to find a "one-stop-shop" for all of the election information you need to exercise your right to vote.

Planned Parenthood provides safe, affordable healthcare to 2.5 million women and men a year. It also provides a safe place for people, especially teenagers and low-income Americans, who have nowhere else to go. Now that policymakers want to defund Planned Parenthood, we must fight to ensure that every American has access to this vital institution. Click here to support Planned Parenthood.

"Karam" means generosity in Arabic. The Karam House is a safe space where Syrian youth who have witnessed and survived the trauma of violence and displacement can learn competitive skills in science, technology, engineering, mathematics, and the arts to prepare them for a brighter future. Click here to invest in the next generation of Syrians.
